## Name Field Exploratory Testing Report
Overview

## This document summarizes the issues discovered during exploratory testing of the Name input field.



## Defects Found

- Period (.) Handling
- Single period (.) is rejected.
- Period with multiple spaces (e.g., " . ") is accepted.
- Multiple consecutive periods (e.g., "............") are accepted.
- Special Character Restrictions
- Most other special characters are rejected.
- Single Letters, Comma, and Period
- Single letters are accepted.
- Commas and periods are accepted inconsistently depending on spacing.
- Birthday Field Issue

- Cannot update the birthday field in certain scenarios (behavior inconsistent).

## Example Behaviors

- . → Rejected
- " . " → Accepted
- "............" → Accepte
- O'Connor → Rejected
- A → Accepted

## impact

- Data Integrity Risk: Inconsistent validation allows invalid names to be submitted.
